pleaserun

This is the pleaserun module

```
  pleaserun {'redis':
    ensure         => present,
    name           => 'redis',
    platform       => 'sysv',
    target_version => 'lsb-3.1',
    program        => '/opt/redis/bin/redis-server',
  } ->

  service { 'redis':
    ensure => running
  }
```

